dataList.appIntro:
Download the Tasty Recipes App and Learn tasty recipes in snack sized cooking videos. Bake the tasty recipes and deliver to your family and friends. 
Tasty Recipes contains variety of easy cooking videos to follow step by by step and cook tasty home recipes.
Be smarter to enjoy better food get tasty recipes daily that anyone can cook through quick step-by-step videos and detailed cooking instructions or baking directions help you learn how to serve beautiful, mouth-watering food to friends, guests, and of course...for your own stomach. Its time to improve your delicious food prep skills through short tips and tricks videos delivered each day.
Tasty Recipes perfect for the foodie, home chef, and anyone wondering what to cook,how to cook at home, serve, and eat! Get inspired for tasty breakfast, brunch, lunch, dinner, dessert, or for tasty snacks! 
search the recipe whenever you're looking for inspiration, search to quickly find what you want, and then save anything you love to your favorite cookbook for future use.
